  chkrootkit-0.37.ebuild :
  New features according to www.chkrootkit.org:
  chklastlog.c fix; chkproc.c improvements; 
  new rootkits detected: 
	OpenBSD rk v1 
	Illogic rootkit  
	SK rootkit  
  new worms detected: 
	Scalper (FreeBSD/Apache chunked encoding worm) 
	Slapper (Apache/mod_ssl Worm) 

